# Colab runbooks and GitHub

Do not `git push` Colab runbook notebooks (e.g. `colab_*.ipynb` or other `.ipynb` protocol/runbooks) to GitHub unless the user has **explicitly** asked to publish or push them in the current task.

Local edits and commits that stay unpushed are fine unless the user asks otherwise.
